   =20
 =20
This  guy!Former Goldman Sachs Group Inc. banker Tim Leissner testified tha=
t after the FBI handed him a grand jury subpoena tied to the 1MDB scandal, =
he consulted a feng shui master to see if more trouble lay ahead over the n=
ext decade.Leissner, the U.S. government=E2=80=99s key witness in the trial=
 of former Goldman colleague Roger Ng over the multibillion-dollar scam to =
loot Malaysia=E2=80=99s wealth fund, told a federal jury on Tuesday that it=
 was Ng who suggested the consultation. He said the master=E2=80=99s report=
 predicted that =E2=80=9CI would have an issue with authorities for the fir=
st half of the 10 years but then it would be resolved.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6Le=
issner told the jury he gave Ng the time and date of his birth for the feng=
 shui reading. He said he and his ex-wife Judy Chan then met with Ng and hi=
s wife, Hwee Bin Lim, at a Hong Kong hotel in 2016 to discuss the report, w=
ith Chan translating for Leissner because he doesn=E2=80=99t read Chinese.L=
eissner testified that he was trying to figure out if he was a target of th=
e U.S. investigation into 1MDB and Goldman Sachs, a subject of the probe or=
 merely a witness.=C2=A0He did all the crimes! Like he took tens of million=
s of dollars of bribes for himself, and he=E2=80=99s wondering if he=E2=80=
=99s merely a witness? And yet here he is, six years later, testifying as a=
 witness. Though after pleading guilty himself.Leissner  has previously tes=
tified that an ex-girlfriend (not Chan!)=C2=A0blackmailed him into buying h=
er a $10 million house by threatening to expose the 1MDB crimes, so I suppo=
se you can have some doubts about the translation. =E2=80=9CThe feng shui m=
aster says you are gonna have trouble with the authorities unless =E2=80=A6=
=C2=A0it says here unless you give all your money to your ex-wife? Well, fe=
ng shui works in mysterious ways.=E2=80=9D Anyway it=E2=80=99s been six=C2=
=A0years since this reading and Leissner is still awaiting sentencing for a=
ll the crimes he has confessed to so there were at least some inaccuracies.
