om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">The tax angle</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere in privateering, here=E2=80=
=99s an <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26886847.2=
62605/aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi5pbnRlcmZheC5jb20udWEvbmV3cy9nZW5lcmFsLzgwNDQ0MS5odG1s/=
607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB1e514ea7" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"item=
scope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !im=
portant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bot=
tom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">apparently real notice</a> from =
Interfax-Ukraine:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><strong>No ne=
ed to declare captured Russian tanks, other equipment of invaders as income=
 =E2=80=93 NAPC</strong></p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ukraine's National=
 Agency for the Protection against Corruption (NAPC) has declared that capt=
ured Russian tanks and other equipment are not subject to declaration.</p><=
p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">"Have you captured a Russian tank or armored pe=
rsonnel carrier and are worried about how to declare it? Keep calm and cont=
inue to defend the Motherland! There is no need to declare the captured Rus=
sian tanks and other equipment, because the cost of this ... does not excee=
d 100 living wages (UAH 248,100)," NAPC's press service said. =E2=80=A6</p>=
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">"Speaking by the letter of the law, combat tro=
phies are not subject to reflection in the declaration for the following re=
asons: they were acquired not as a result of the conclusion of any type of =
transaction, but in connection with the full-scale aggression of the Russia=
n Federation on February 24, 2022 against the independent and sovereign Ukr=
ainian state as a continuation the insidious attack of the Russian Federati=
on on Ukraine launched in 2014. Thanks to the courage and victory of the de=
fenders of the Ukrainian state, enemy military equipment usually comes to y=
ou already destroyed and disabled, which makes it impossible to evaluate it=
 in accordance with the law On the valuation of property, property rights a=
nd professional valuation activities in Ukraine. Therefore, it is also impo=
ssible to find out how much such property costs,=E2=80=9D the NACP said.</p=
></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This strikes me as sensible tax =
policy. For one thing, taxing anything tends to discourage that thing, and =
clearly the Ukrainian government wants to encourage its citizens to capture=
 Russian tanks. For another thing, surely the stated reasoning is correct a=
nd it is hard to get a market value for a disabled Russian tank; if you can=
=E2=80=99t sell it in a ready market it is a bit harsh to have to pay taxes=
 on it. Presumably the main motive for this press release is not so much to=
 get the tax policy right but rather to demonstrate some incredible wartime=
 sangfroid, but the tax policy also seems right.</p><table class=3D"header"=
 width=3D"100%" border=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" cellpadding=3D"0">
<tr>
<td class=3D"body-header-container" style=3D"border-collapse: collapse; mso=
-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt;">
<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">I must study electronic trading so that my son may get into crystals =
and run my ESG department</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here=E2=80=99s Thomas Peterffy=E2=80=
=99s story:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Before building a n=
et worth of $21.5 billion on Wall Street, Thomas grew up in communist Hunga=
ry, immigrated to the U.S. at the age of 21 knowing no English, and saved u=
p to buy a seat on the American Stock Exchange. He became an early player i=
n electronic trading, building a company that used computers to transact in=
 financial markets and eventually evolved into a broker that sells professi=
onal-quality trading software to individual investors and money managers, i=
ncluding hedge funds. He=E2=80=99d achieved the fantasy of amassing an unim=
aginable fortune.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here=E2=80=
=99s his son <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26886=
847.262605/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2ZlYXR1cmVzLzIwMjItMDMt=
MDIvYmlsbGlvbmFpcmUtd2FsbC1zdHJlZXQtaGVpci13aWxsaWFtLXBldGVyZmZ5LXRha2VzLWV=
zZy1yb2xlLXRvLWZpeC1jYXBpdGFsaXNtP2NtcGlkPUJCRDAzMDIyMl9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV=
9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIyMDMwMiZ1dG1fY=
2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBf4790877" itemprop=3D"St=
oryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000;=
 text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-=
color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Will =
Peterffy=E2=80=99s story</a>:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">H=
e=E2=80=99s been a ranch hand in Colorado; an organic farm worker in Califo=
rnia; a student of yoga, sound therapy, and Chinese medicine; a board membe=
r for an environmental advocacy organization; and a post-production associa=
te for a 10-part documentary series on =E2=80=9Carchetypal astrology.=E2=80=
=9D He served time at two investment firms, for about nine months apiece, b=
ut those stints left him =E2=80=9Cheart-crushed=E2=80=9D and pushed him in =
2016 to go, with his dog Bowie, from New York to New Mexico in hopes of abs=
orbing the healing powers of the desert. =E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 1=
6px 0;">In late November he visited friends for dinner at their regenerativ=
e farm. A citrine crystal, believed to symbolize positivity and new beginni=
ngs, sat nearby as he feasted on braised lamb shoulder, mashed potatoes, ar=
ugula, beet sauerkraut, and a punchy fermented hot sauce=E2=80=94a meal his=
 friends prepared using only crops and animals raised on their farm, except=
 for a bit of clarified butter and a few glugs of olive oil. =E2=80=A6</p><=
p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">More than two years earlier he=E2=80=99d joined=
 his father=E2=80=99s company, a giant trading platform called Interactive =
Brokers Group Inc. Rather than become a sales rep or data analyst, he carve=
d out a role more simpatico with his worldview. Not unlike when he was 7 an=
d made the case for getting a pet ferret, he pitched his dad on a big idea:=
 that he could become the company=E2=80=99s first director of environmental=
, social, and governance (ESG) affairs, helping to make the firm a better s=
teward of the Earth and society. Interactive Brokers would reduce its envir=
onmental footprint, boost gender and racial diversity, and, in the triple-b=
ottom-line spirit, draw a whole new set of younger customers who want to in=
vest in companies doing the same. =E2=80=9CWe=E2=80=99ve been saturated wit=
h this idea that we are separate=E2=80=94we are separate from each other, w=
